snippet.title: Stack Up! (or dive trying) Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game on Steam at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1297090/ 
Join the official Discord server: https://discord.gg/j4G8h4n

Stack Up (or dive trying) is an endless platformer with increasing difficulty. The objective is simple: go higher. Fall in the water once and you are done. Precise movement and smart planning are key, reorganize the objects at your disposal to build your way up. Some objects are harmless, some helpful and others... well a little bit less.
